<html><body>
<style>
.emailbody {
    font-family: Arial,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,sans-serif; 
    border: 2px solid skyblue;
    padding:10px;
    border-radius:10px;
}
.spacey tr td {
    padding:5px;
}}
</style>
<div class="emailbody">
    <table class="spacey">
    <tr><td>Error No: &nbsp;</td>
        <td><b>{$req.errNo|html}</b></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Comment by: &nbsp; </td>
        <td>
            <a href="{$baseURL}v/FindPerson.htm?uid={$req.requester}" title="access the profile of this user, if one exists">
                <span class="red">{$req.modUser|html}</span>
            </a>
        </td></tr>
    <tr><td>Comment: &nbsp;</td>
        <td>{$req.comment|html}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>URI: &nbsp;</td>
        <td><a html="{$req.uri|html}">{$req.uri|html}</a></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Date: &nbsp;</td>
        <td>{$req.modTime|date("MMM dd, YYYY")}</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p>User <a href="{$baseURL}v/FindPerson.htm?uid={$admin.uid}">{$admin.name|html}</a> is a <b>Super Admin</b> of the Weaver console, so you get a copy of this user feedback.</p>
</div>

